This program uses CMake.  It has been tested on Mac OSX 10.6.8, should work on Linux/BSD, 
and will require more work to port to Windows.

Required libraries/programs:
-cmake (>= 2.6, only tested with 2.8.8)
-libnfc (>= 1.6.0, only tested with 1.6.0-rc1)
-libusb (for libnfc)
-PCSC libraries (included with OSX, libpcsclite on Linux/BSD, with Microsoft SDK on Windows)

To build:

mkdir build
cd build
cmake ..
make
(optionally) make install


